    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that serves as a benchmark for preservation. This car has been kept in a climate-controlled garage under a breathable cover, ensuring the factory paint remains in flawless, concours-level condition with a deep, mirror-like luster. There are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks on the body, and the alloy wheels are entirely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the leather upholstery retains its original matte finish and supple texture, completely devoid of bolster wear or creasing. It has never been smoked in and has never carried pets. Every switch, dial, and digital display functions with the tactile precision of a new vehicle. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule by brand specialists. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting its history of fair-weather use only. This sale includes the full set of original keys, all factory manuals, and a binder of service receipts. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
      "price": 44500.0,
